 * See: https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/issues/xyz
 *
 * The problem occurs with code like:
 * ```
 * if ("a" == "b") {
 * } else if ("b" == "c") else {
 * }
 * ```
 * Where `else if ("b" == "c") else` has an empty THEN block after the condition.
 */
